<header><h1>Scrambled Eggs</h1></header>
<p>Eggs are one of my favourite foods.Here is receipe for deliciously scrambled eggs</p>

<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
<li>2 Eggs</li>
<li>1 tbs butter</li>
<li>2 tbs cream</li>
</ul>

<h2>Method</h2>
<ol>
<li>Melt butter over frying pan in medium heat</li>
<li>Gently mix the eggs and cream in bowl.</li>
<li>Once butter has menlted add cream and eggs.</li>
<li>Using spatula fold the eggs from the edge of the pan to centre every 20 seconds.</li>
<li>When the eggs are moist ,remove the heat</li>
</ol>
